{
  "text": "Adoptive transfer of OT II and CBir1 Tg T cells and induction of colitis. As previously described, CFSE-labeled or unlabeled CD4 + T cells were injected i.v. into groups of five RAG \ue032/\ue032 mice housed in SPF or germfree condition. In some experiments, certain groups of the OT II T cell recipients were given OVA-expressing E. coli or TET-expressing E. coli into the colon weekly. OVA-expressing E. coli and TET-expressing E. coli were generated as described previously [CITATION_1] . 2 mo later, the mice were sacrificed and histopathology was examined.",
